  Hou7-su7 theh8 choa2 pit lai5 hou7 i, i chiu7-sia2: ¡§Sou2 thiaN3 e5 Hui7-bi2. Kiu5-li2 sia3-bian2 goa2 e5 choe7. Goa2 tui3-li2 chin put-chu7. Goan7-li2 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 thoe3 goa2 ai-kiu5, in-ui7 goa2 i2-keng u7 chhim-chhim hoan2-hoe2 chai-choe7. Cheng5 goa2 chun5 kan-kui2 e5 sim phian3-li2, phian3 Siong7-te3. Sit8-chai7 chin kai-si2, taN chit-si5 goa2 tui3 sim-te2 chhim-chhim thong3-hoe2, hoat-sim sin3 Chu2 Ia5-sou. Kiu5 I un-tian2 chin2-kiu3 goa2 e5 leng5-hun5. Goa2 ng3-bang7 e7-tit kap li2 saN-kiN3 ti7 thiN. Chong2-si7 goa2 iau2 u7 chit8-tiam2 e5 ng3-bang7, chiu7-si7 bang7 li2 kho2-leng5 iau2 ti7 se3-kan. Na7-si7 chit e5 ng3-bang7 si7 chin poh8, kiam2-chhai2 si7 goa2 e5 gong7-siuN7. Chong2-si7 goa2 i2-keng chai, goa2 e7 siu7 hoat-lut8 e5 chhai5-phoaN3. Goa2 bo5 lou7 thang ka-ti7 se2-chheng. Ah! Sou2 thiaN3--e5. Siat-su2 li2 na7 iau2-oah8, li2 kiam2 be7 tai3-liam7 tioh8 chhou-hoe7 ti7 soaN-teng2 ban2 Pek-hap8-hoe e5 si5. Kiam2 be7 siuN7 tioh8 choe3-hoe2 kou3 A-pa ti7 peN7-chhng5. Kiam2 be7 siuN7 tioh8 goa2 tui-chhoe7 li2, chhoe7 li2 ti7 Hun5-lam5-siaN5-goa7 e5 chit8 e5 hiuN-chng e5 sio2-tek-ui5 e5 cheng5-keng2. Ah! Na7 koh siuN7 hiah e5 tiN-bit8 e5 ai3-cheng5, goa2 e5 sim sit8-chai7 beh piak-lih8.¡¨ Sia2 kau3 chia bak8-sai2 hou3 m7-khui tit8-tit8 hau2 chhut--lai5, chiu7 khi2-lai5 kiaN5-oa2 au7-piah thang-a2-kiN beh theh8 bin7-kin chhit bak8-sai2. Hut-jian5 taN-thau5 khoaN3 thang-a2-goa7 u7 chit8 e5 lang5, hit e5 lang5-iaN2 chhin-chhiuN7 Hui7-bi2! I bo5 i3-sek kio3 chin toa7-siaN ¡§Hui7-bi2¡¨! Chong2-si7 hit e5 lang5-iaN2 chu7 an2-ni bo5 khi3. I chin m7-goan7 chu7 chheng7 khun3-saN khui-mng5 jiok chhut--lai5. Ko2-jian5 u7 chit8 e5 lang5 teh chau2, ji5-chhiaN2 si7 cha-bou2-lang5 e5 khoan2. In-ui7 goeh8 bo5 kng, tak tioh8 chioh8-thau5 soa3 phak-loh8-khi3, khi2 nau2 pin5-hiat, kou3 me5 e5 hou7-su7 kin2-lai5, ia7 kap hit e5 teh chau2 e5 lang5 ia7 oat to3-tng2--lai5. Ka7 i kng jip8 peN7-pang5. Theng5 oa2 chiaN5-khek ku2 chia cheng-sin5. Sim chin giau5-gi