  Kau3 chit8-le2-pai3 au7 chiu7 koh siu7 tiau3 kau3 hoat-iN7 siu7 u5-sim2. U5-sim2 koaN tai7-seng mng7 i e5 seN3-mia5, ni5-hoe3, chu7-chi2. Khak-jin7 chit-e5 lang5 ko2-jian5 si7 Tan5 Khun-hong, Tan5 Hok-choan5 si7 ke2-mia5, it-it chu7-jin7. Ia7 ka-ti7 chu7-jin7 si7 ui7 kiaN choe7, sou2-i2 chiah to5-choe7 lai5 Siong7-hai2. Thang-kong2 10 hun e5 8, 9 i ka-ti7 seng5-jin7 Hui7-bi2 e5 si2 si7 i ka7 i that loh8 khi3 e5. Put-ko3 u7 kui2-na7 tiam2 thang koh tiau-cha chiu7-si7. (1) Si7 ok-i3, a2-si7 bu5-i3. (2) Si7 i chit8 e5 ka7 i that lai5 ti3-si2, a2-si7 iau2 u7 pang-chhiu2. Na7 siat-su2 u7 pang-chhiu2, chiu7 piN3-choe3 ok-i3, kiong7-bou5. (3) ChaiN2-iuN7 e7 biat8-si. An2-ni si7 poah8 loh8-chui2 si2, a2-si7 ti7 pat8-ui7 i2-keng ka7 i chhong3-si2, chiah kng lai5 thiam ti7 Lian5-hoe-ti5, ke2 choe3 poah8-loh8-chui2 si2. In-ui7 si7 biat8-si, sou2-i2 lang5 poah8-loh8-chui2 ka-ti7 kou-bo5, ia7 bo5 lang5 lai5 po3 keng2-chhat. Tui3 chit 3 tiam2 iau2 boe7 beng5. 
