  Chhoa3 sian-siN te7 6 kam2 si7 kam2-kak Siu3-chhun tui3 chit-chan5 su7 ia7-si7 chit8 e5 Chu2-kak, chek-si5 kio3 chit8 e5 heng5-keng2 khi3 kio3 Siu3-chhun lai5. Kio3 i lai5 Lian5-hoe-ti5-piN kiam2-cheng3. Heng5-keng2 khi3 e5 si5 chhoe7 bo5. To3-tng2 lai5 po3-ko3, kong2 lai7-bin7 chhoe7 bo5 lang5, pang5-keng chi2 u7 chit8 e5 eN-a2 teh-hau2, chin ki5-koai3, it-hoat kho2-gi5 chit e5 lang5 u7 choe7-hiam5. Sou2-i2 beng7-leng7 choan5-chhu3-theh8 lai7-goa7 chong2 sou-cha. Tauh ti2 Siu3-chhun tui3 to2-ui7 khi3? Kau3-boe2 chiah hoat-kian3 i si2 ti7 au7 hoe-hng5 e5 kou2-chiN2-te2. In-ui7 lang5 thoa Khun-hong beh lai5 kiam2-cheng3 e5 si5, i iaN2 tioh8 Khun-hong bin7 ti3 chhau2-lap-a2, chhiu2 hou7 lang5 pak8 iap-au7, eng7 chhiu2-khau3 khau3 leh. Siu3-chhun toa7-kiaN, chai si2 lah. Koh-si7 choan5-kok ti-mia5 e5 Chhoa3 cheng-tham3 choan-an3 cheng-pan7. Chai hoat-bong2 lan5-to5. I ka-ti7 chai, chha5 kau3-boe2 chu2-hoan7 m7-si7 Khun-hong. Chu2-hoan7 si7 i pun2-sin, Khun-hong si7 bu5-i3, na7-si7 iu2-i3 chun5 sat-jin5, koh tit8-chiap e5 ti3-si2 si7 tui3 i e5 heng5-tong7. Sou2-i2 kau3-chia i siuN7 khi2 hoat-teng5 hian7-si3, m7-tat8-tioh8 si2 tiam3 chhu3-nih khah tit8. Sou2-i2 chiong Eng5-chong(eN-a2) ka7 i hiat tiam3 bin5-chhng5, than3 lang5 bo5 chu3-i3 chu7 an2-ni khi3 thiau3 kou2-chiN2. I m7-si7 eng7 thiau3, i si7 eng7 tian-to3-thau5-chai chai loh8 khi3. Sou2-i2 kou khi2--lai5 i2-keng koe3-khui3 nge7-nge7, si5-kan ia7 i2-keng koe3 30 hun khah ke. Thau5-khak chai ti7 chiN2-te2 e5 lou5-kou-moai5, sou2-i2 chit8 chhui3 chit8 phiN7, si3-ke3 long2 si7 lou5-kou-moai5 that tiN7-tiN7. Tui3 u7 chui2-to7, chit e5 cheN2 han2 tit eng7 chin chhim, chui2 ia7 u7 chhau3-bi7, kau3-boe2 kiu3 be7 oah8. Na7-si7 tong5-si5 sou-cha, ti7 Hui7-bi2 e5 pang5-keng u7 hoat-kian3 tioh8 Hui7-bi2 chu7-sat e5 ui5-gian5-chng7, che-si7 chin ki5-koai3 e5 su7. 
